    <diagram id="wkasQ50eaeU6SD_mDHHj" name="Entity Model Description">
        <mxGraphModel dx="2052" dy="1397" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1600" pageHeight="1200" math="0" shadow="0">
            <root>
                <mxCell id="0"/>
                <mxCell id="1" parent="0"/>
                <mxCell id="nKRXAdr2OOU9JWNcl3Ly-1" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Entities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Authority&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(reference)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The Authority node represents a finalized and approved document such as an RFC or other specification. An Authority may be functionally changed by only another Authority; corrections to an existing Authority are represented by Errata or an ErrataSet.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;AuthorityDraft&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(reference)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The AuthorityDraft node represents an in-process document such as an Internet-Draft or other specification. This is top-level node representing any in-process version of the draft.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Revision&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(reference)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;A Revision node represents a single version of an in-process document.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Errata&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(reference)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;An Errata node represents a correction (technical or typographic) to a finalized and approved Authority. Errata may not make functional changes to an Authority document. Errata references may be a centralized ID number, a reference in a specific repository (e.g., GitHub Issue), or other identifiable reference.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;ErrataSet&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(reference)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;An ErrataSet node represents a collection of Errata. An ErrataSet may be used in the periodic publication of an Authority to ensure the text is representative of the true meaning of the Authority.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;ControllingOrg&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(name)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;A ControllingOrg node represents an organization responsible for the content or publication of an Authority. A given ControllingOrg may be a child of another ControllingOrg (e.g., a Working Group of the IETF, etc.).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Protocol&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(name)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;A Protocol node is a high-level representation of a family of protocols.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;ProtocolVersion&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(versionedName)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;A ProtocolVersion node represents a specific version of a protocol. All protocols must have at least one ProtocolVersion node defined.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;ProtocolFeature&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(name)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;A ProtocolFeature node represents an element of a Protocol that is of interest to be tracked or discovered&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Revision&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;(reference)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;A Revision node represents a single version of an in-process document.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="120" width="480" height="1040" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="nKRXAdr2OOU9JWNcl3Ly-2" value="Entity Model Description" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=35;fontStyle=1" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="40" width="480" height="60" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="C8J497onc_pKKVwW1gyu-1" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Relationships&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;CONTROLS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;ControllingOrg&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;→&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Authority&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;ControllingOrg&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;→&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;AuthorityDraft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The CONTROLS relationship represents the organization that is responsible and/or publishes a given document.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;HAS_CHILD_ORG&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;ControllingOrg&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;→&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;ControllingOrg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The HAS_CHILD_ORG relationship represents a parent-child relationship between ControllingOrgs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;DRAFTED_BY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;→&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;AuthorityDraft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The DRAFTED_BY relationship indicates the preceding draft document for a given Authority.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;HAS_REVISION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;→&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Revision&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The HAS_REVISION relationship represents linkage of an AuthorityDraft to one or more Revisions. Typically, an AuthorityDraft will have many Revisions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;REFERENCES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → Authority&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → AuthorityDraft&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → Revision&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → Authority&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → AuthorityDraft&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → Revision&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Revision → Authority&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Revision → AuthorityDraft&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Revision → Revision&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The REFERENCES relationship represents upstream references between documents. REFERENCES must be assigned a subtype: &lt;i&gt;normative&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;for those references that are required for a given Authority to function; &lt;i&gt;informative&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;for those references that only provide additional (e.g., background or historical) information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="600" y="120" width="480" height="1040" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="C8J497onc_pKKVwW1gyu-2" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;UPDATES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → Authority&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → Authority&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → AuthorityDraft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Revision → Revision&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The UPDATES relationship represents a document that makes functional changes to a specification defined in another document. An AuthorityDraft must only update an Authority while the draft is still in-process; once a draft is approved, this relationship must be removed.&amp;nbsp; A Revision may only update another Revision.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;OBSOLETES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → Authority&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → AuthorityDraft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → AuthorityDraft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The OBSOLETES relationship represents an Authority that defines a specification that foundationally replaces another specification.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The OBSOLETES relationship may also represent an Authority or AuthorityDraft that directly replaces another Authority or AuthorityDraft (e.g., moving from a draft-author-* document to a draft-ietf-* document in IETF WGs). This does not apply to direct&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Authority → AuthorityDraft DRAFTED_BY&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;relationships.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;EXTENDS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → Authority&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → AuthorityDraft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → Authority&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → AuthorityDraft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The EXTENDS relationship represents an Authority that defines new functionality that is related to another specification. This relationship is used when a specification does not directly change another specification.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1120" y="120" width="480" height="1040" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="RYo3TlFaD4Msp3YL0J3Z-1" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;CORRECTS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Errata → Authority&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;ErrataSet → Authority&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2 style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The CORRECTS relationship represents a typographical or technical correction to a published Authority. Errata cannot provide functional updates to a specification.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;CONTAINS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;ErrataSet → Errata&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The CONTAINS relationship represents a collection of Errata in an ErrataSet. This construct is often used for publication purposes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;DEFINES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → ProtocolVersion&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Authority → ProtocolFeature&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → ProtocolVersion&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;AuthorityDraft → ProtocolFeature&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The DEFINES relationship represents relationships between a given document and a protocol. Linkage to ProtocolVersion describe specific protocol semantics (e.g., PKCE impacting OAuth 2.0). Linkage to ProtocolFeature describe categories of features that should be tracked together (e.g., PKCE relating to Client Verification and Authorization Code Flow).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;?IMPLEMENTS?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;ProtocolVersion → Protocol&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;The IMPLEMENTS relationship represents a particular version of a protocol related to the family of protocols (e.g., OAuth 2.0 as a representative of OAuth).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1640" y="120" width="480" height="1040" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
            </root>
        </mxGraphModel>
    </diagram>
